---
import Link from "./ui/link.astro";
---

<div class="bg-white p-8 md:px-20 md:py-20 mt-100 mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center">
  <h2 class="text-black text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
    Connect to anything
  </h2>
  <p class="text-black text-lg font-bold mt-4 text-slate-600">
    Connect to most databases or anything with a REST, GraphQL or gRPC API. CodeBlocks empowers you to work with all of your data sources seamlessly in one app.

    How you store data is up to you. By default, nothing is stored in CodeBlocks. When a query is run, the CodeBlocks backend proxies the request to your backend. No more ETL-ing data around!
  </p>
  <div class="flex mt-5">
    <Link href="#" size="md" block>View our native integrations</Link>
  </div>
</div>
